'''Takatalant''' di [[Katalunya]].

Aseqdec n Tkatalant yeẓẓa iẓuran-is yerna simma simma la ttnernin di [[Katalunya]]. Di tallit-nni ideg [[Franco]] yeṭṭef [[Spanyul]] yegdel-itt, maca xas akken, tedder deg yilsawen n Ikatalanen . 
Di tmendawt(Constitution) taspenyult n 1978, Tameslayt-a tuγal d tunṣibt di Katalunya d Tegzirin Baléares daγen di temnaḍt n [[Valansya]], dinna ssawalen-as “Tavanlansyant”. Tasekla s Tkatalant teğuğğeg, ayen din n yedlisen i d-yettrusun di tsedlisin, ula deg isupermarciyen znuzun-ten. 
Deg iberdan ukeṛṛus ipanuten ttwarun yakk s Tkatalant, ttwarun ula s Tkastilant ([[Taspenyult]]) maca seddaw n Tkatalant. Tisdawiyin smenyafent taγuri (leqraya) s Tkatalant, tuget n tezrawin tgen-tent yinelmaden s tmeslayt-a, ula deg isura n sinima isutitrajen tgen-ten s Tkatalant.

Tilibizyuwat d yilγagduden-nniḍen ttmeslayen s Tkatalant, seg imeẓyanen alamma d imγaren zemren yakk yikatalanen ad slen, ad walin neγ ad γren ayen i sen-yehwan s Tkatalant.

